）。  \r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　5 　　月　　31　　日\r\n                       書記官  張裕昌","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SJEV/111%2c%e9%87%8d%e7%b0%a1%2c685%2c20220531%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SJEV,111,重簡,685,20220531,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"重簡","JNO":"685","JDATE":"20220531","JTITLE":"清償借款等"}